snippet.title: Codename Mallow Death Compilation
snippet.description:
Demo - https://www.codenamemallow.com/

Codename Mallow is an adrenaline-charged versus multiplayer game with armless melee battles, one-hit-kill weaponry, and wildly unpredictable stages. Duel for Ninja Supremacy with up to 4 friends in local or online play. Demo available NOW!

Itch.io - https://ancalabro.itch.io/codename-ma...
Twitter - https://twitter.com/ancalabro
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/ancalabro/
Discord - https://discord.com/invite/taY8nXW
